  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Unfolds with Every Flip of the Coin</h2>Flip Coin is a captivating game where you navigate through various environments by flipping a coin. Carefully maneuver the coin to reach your destination and complete each level!<br><br><br><strong>Intuitive Controls</strong><br>Use simple and intuitive controls to flip the coin towards the goal. Even beginners can quickly grasp the gameplay mechanics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/d9383879866447451e3fb2ea19a2ea97.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=162 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/951c7cc1483244e4432948da0a631923.poster.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/951c7cc1483244e4432948da0a631923.webm?t=1721224879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/951c7cc1483244e4432948da0a631923.mp4?t=1721224879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Variety of Levels</strong><br>Experience fresh challenges across multiple themed levels, each offering a unique adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/5484f5b52f0320f6b85d05e116e42eab.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Sense of Achievement</strong><br>The sense of accomplishment you feel upon completing each level is one of the game’s greatest appeals. Master each level and witness your growth.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072530/extras/c3891e48531f85b4061bcad230e65f60.avif?t=1721224879\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
